<subSubSection id="D9F16554FF99BA35B4AEFF45B104F775" pageId="37" pageNumber="656" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="915436DFFF99BA35B4AEFF45B104F775" blockId="37.[186,1394,1454,2275]" pageId="37" pageNumber="656">
<emphasis id="A39FEACDFF99BA35B4AEFF45B007F788" bold="true" box="[188,545,2085,2118]" pageId="37" pageNumber="656">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. The species nearly qualifies as Vulnerable, as it is rare and has been recorded from few locations in highly fragmented habitats that are undergoing further degradation, due to shifting agriculture and wood harvesting.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
